---
// About.astro - ULTRACTION About Section (Nova Construct Design Pattern)
---

<section class="border-b border-primary/20 dark:border-primary/20">
  <div class="p-6 md:p-12 lg:p-16 max-w-7xl mx-auto">
    <h2 class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest mb-8 md:mb-12 opacity-60">About Us</h2>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6 md:gap-8">
      <!-- About Us -->
      <div class="border-t border-primary/20 dark:border-primary/20 pt-6">
        <span class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-accent opacity-30 font-heading mb-4 block">01</span>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold uppercase mb-3 font-heading">Who We Are</h3>
        <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed opacity-80">
          ULTRACTION General Contracting LLC is a premier construction company based in the UAE, specializing in delivering exceptional building solutions for residential and commercial projects.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Our Approach -->
      <div class="border-t border-primary/20 dark:border-primary/20 pt-6">
        <span class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-accent opacity-30 font-heading mb-4 block">02</span>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold uppercase mb-3 font-heading">Our Approach</h3>
        <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed opacity-80">
          We combine innovative construction techniques with proven methodologies to ensure every project is completed on time, within budget, and to the highest standards.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Our Values -->
      <div class="border-t border-primary/20 dark:border-primary/20 pt-6">
        <span class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-accent opacity-30 font-heading mb-4 block">03</span>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold uppercase mb-3 font-heading">Our Values</h3>
        <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed opacity-80">
          Quality, integrity, and customer satisfaction are at the core of everything we do. We build lasting relationships through transparent communication and exceptional service.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Our Expertise -->
      <div class="border-t border-primary/20 dark:border-primary/20 pt-6">
        <span class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-accent opacity-30 font-heading mb-4 block">04</span>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold uppercase mb-3 font-heading">Our Expertise</h3>
        <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed opacity-80">
          With years of experience and a team of skilled professionals, we have the expertise to handle projects of any scale, from renovations to large-scale construction.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
